{"talk":{"id":2127,"name":"Ameenah Gurib-Fakim: Humble plants that hide surprising secrets","description":"(NOTE: Ameenah Gurib-Fakim stepped down as president of Mauritius in March 2018, following accusations that she misused a credit card given to her by a nonprofit. Read \"Criticisms & Updates\" below for more details.) In this intriguing talk, biologist Ameenah Gurib-Fakim introduces us to rare plant species from isolated islands and regions of Africa. Meet the shape-shifting benjoin; the baume de l'ile plate, which might offer a new treatment for asthma; and the iconic baobab tree, which could hold the key to the future of food. Plus: monkey apples.","slug":"ameenah_gurib_fakim_humble_plants_that_hide_surprising_secrets","recorded_at":"2014-10-27 00:00:00","published_at":"2014-11-04 16:03:07","updated_at":"2020-09-28 21:39:54","viewed_count":1031237,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":324,"name":"TEDGlobal 2014"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/7aeb7073ee393b188627d436031e10fa090bc885_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/7aeb7073ee393b188627d436031e10fa090bc885_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/7aeb7073ee393b188627d436031e10fa090bc885_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/7aeb7073ee393b188627d436031e10fa090bc885_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/d5392a4becfeddb12318d16f9b3e66eea70449c1_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/AmeenahGuribFakim_2014G-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":7014083,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/AmeenahGuribFakim_2014G-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":19452120,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/Ame